save fst

Source: R/save_fst.R
save_fst.Rd

write R data frame as fst..

Usage

save_fst(
  Object_to_save,
  Name_to_save,
  output = "1. Ingelezen data/",
  dataloc,
  session_info = FALSE,
  ...
)

Arguments

Object_to_save

Data frame.

Name_to_save

File name to write without extension.

output

Location on network drive, depending on the value of branch "G:/DSZ/SA2016/Datasets/Output/(branch)/"

dataloc

Location on network drive, having as root "G:/DSZ/SA2016/Datasets/"

session_info

Default: FALSE. Whether to save session info to same directory.

...

dot parameters to parse to write_fst
